name: Umezawa Yukari no Taikyoku Igo: Heisei Kiin II
overview: Umezawa Yukari no Taikyoku Igo: Heisei Kiin II is an igo game endorsed by the Go player Umezawa Yukari. The game features 4 different difficulty levels, 5 different boards, different backgrounds & cursors and also a 2 players vs mode. The game features complete Go tutorials with videos of Umezawa Yukari explaining the rules and movements.
